          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">A </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements" translate="true">Motion-Dimension FB</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> defines the Angle or Linear Distance between two Parts that are joined with a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Pin-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Pin-Joint</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> or a </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Slide-Joint" styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Slide-Joint</link><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The Motion-Dimension value between the two Parts is continually updated by motion-values &apos;passed to&apos; the Motion-Dimension FB from other FBs at the input-connector with &apos;wires&apos;.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><line style="height:1px; color:#ff6600;" /></para>
